project_SBS is the "Sunday Bloody Sunday" project made by Alexis Guiho, David Baron & Adrien Alexandre.
It's a Zombie Shooter developed in C# with XNA library.
More informations on : www.projet-sbs.fr/game.html

To run the game, you must have :
Microsoft .NET Framework 4
Microsoft XNA Framework Redistributable 4.0

To launch the game, go in :
\projet_sbs\Projet\Sunday Bloody Sunday\Sunday Bloody Sunday\Sunday Bloody Sunday\bin\x86\Debug
and open on Sunday Bloody Sunday.exe

Current manual of the game :
        /*
         * TitleSreen : Press "Enter" to start the game
         * MainSreen (the game) :
         *      Use arrows to move the player
         *      Press "N" to shoot
         *      Press "Escape" to pause the game
		 *		Press "1" to activate the IA generation
		 *		Press "2" to activate the COOP mode
         * MenuSreen :
         *     Press "Enter" to select an option :
         *           - Resume
         *           - Weapons inventory (doesn't work!)
         *           - Exit
         */